{"tid":506323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★原來合法！露宿者以公園為登記地址，獲法庭裁定有效","createTime":"2017-12-22T05:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-22T12:05:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"55663f325cb4ed07ad9f44fc027241e99415795e","tid":506323,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"其中一家四口住在石澳的張生被她質疑登記地址不存在，張親自出庭解釋指住在寮屋，需經小路進入。<br />\n姚指寮屋屬非法建築，住址不合法，要求選舉事務處設指引，以界定可接受的選民登記地址。惟處方回應指地址是否合法非處方所關注，只要證明選民居住在上址便可，<span style=\"color: red;\">過往有露宿者以公園為登記地址，獲法庭裁定有效</span>。馬官其後慨嘆指香港居住問題非常嚴重，認同處方解釋，駁回投訴。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150909/19288180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150909%2F19288180&d=LX3jfKltR5G0quaevRKfHKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=944549bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20150909%2F19288180&h=e166f816\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20150909/19288180</a>"},{"pid":"3642acb9762d9d799028b82d6ade8252278727c1","tid":506323,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1e547518452f1afb66da3ae346c630e52ca84d2","tid":506323,"uid":19454,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"咁 金拱門更加合法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f274b949c2fd218ca1d8a5242187c5065b22df76","tid":506323,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T06:03:04.000Z","